               She has a group of six direct reports and about 6 other support 
               people in their "CSCW project." Objective is to introduce new 
               technology for collaboration etc. in internal "test-bed" 
               situations, trying to work for improvement of group-work 
               productivity within the Boeing Aerospace.  (Sound relevant??)
               Told her at some length about AUGMENT, integrated architecture, 
